{"tid":342143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]從馬桶撈初生嬰兒 80後護士畫出醫院見聞","createTime":"2017-07-31T11:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T11:10:18.000Z","uid":65368,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"828897fa3b37a827bd101b7bf478ce004a1adf28","tid":342143,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"註冊護士及助產士Cosy已入行約7年，有畫畫習慣的她，將經歷化成漫畫，放在Facebook專頁「小護士闖江湖」，反應不俗。她又剛出版了《小護士闖江湖--學護辛酸私曰記》，揭開鮮為人知的行內見聞。<br />\n<br />\n於2011年畢業的Cosy成為註冊護士後，再進修18個月成為助產士。那18個月中，她需要調節心態，面對不同環境，<br />\n<br />\n那時需要不斷轉環境，因要嘗試不同部門，有產前、產後、產房及門診。在這幾個地方轉來轉去，可能每兩個月便轉一次，適應了一個地方後便立即轉去另一個地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n始終肩負起的，是媽媽與小寶寶的生命，責任重大，壓力也自然不少：<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企睡覺，也會聽到嬰兒心跳的噗噗聲。<br />\n<br />\n但Cosy認為婦產科仍然是醫院入面，最開心的部門：<br />\n<br />\n雖然都有不開心的事，但大部分都是好開心的。<br />\n<br />\n危急事件在產房內也時有發生，Cosy說<br />\n<br />\n我比較黑仔，真係好多嘢都見過。<br />\n<br />\n例如她最驚生育過的媽媽不聽叮囑，仍堅持上洗手間大便，<br />\n<br />\n生第二胎的媽媽可以生得好快，BB可以用『飛出來』來形容。BB出生前，頭部會壓着媽媽的腸，所以媽媽會有想要大便的感覺，我常千叮萬囑媽媽這時不要上洗手間大便。但總有些人不聽話，於是便要把BB從屎塔撈上來，真的讓人好崩潰，一年總有好幾次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p0ygtar8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp0ygtar8&h=891b4537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/08ej3aow\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F08ej3aow&h=47dee837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇條女fb/ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44231536992c1b88699f28081ab71edee0e5e3f6","tid":342143,"uid":28619,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想入院now"},{"pid":"02d860f033429b42176700412821761b7d10dfd4","tid":342143,"uid":87428,"like":55,"dislike":4,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"愈大波愈有母愛<br />\n你見個個無波既,通常又黑心,又賤,又港女"},{"pid":"5696b61a33ae13bf88273045303f6f5aa7892c98","tid":342143,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"想重新出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695f7dce1585853127d06d6fadb87a7960ab4966","tid":342143,"uid":83097,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"D回覆痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4d20b31a02dfa099c63fa5dd4e5e492d100460","tid":342143,"uid":68003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"世界級女友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比d 醫生食Q 曬"},{"pid":"198dc0d29049479dd0156c735bb5d88fb3efb587","tid":342143,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愈大波愈有母愛<br />\n你見個個無波既,通常又黑心,又賤,又港女</blockquote><br />\nagger，一睇就知條女好有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d3cd4696fc79d1112c28bbf87b8606c2818d12","tid":342143,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"好撚大波"},{"pid":"3f77613e34c976cafa1fa0feb6fa5999bb314cba","tid":342143,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 